<h1 id="onboarding-checklist">Onboarding Checklist</h1>
<p>Check list for new joiners to the Platform Operations team</p>

<ul>
<li>Give users Platform Operations Confluence page links and documentation to read

<ol>
<li><a href="https://hmcts.github.io/#the-hmcts-way">The HMCTS Way</a></li>
<li><a href="https://tools.hmcts.net/confluence/display/DTSPO/Team+Structure">Team Structure</a></li>
</ol></li>
<li>Add the new joiner to Platform Operations group in Slack</li>
<li>Send out relevant meeting invites for Stand ups, Retro, Show and Tells</li>
<li>Send PlatOps Jira board link to new joiner</li>
<li>Setup catch up calls with Team leads if needed</li>
<li>Verify the new joiner has an entry in <a href="https://github.com/hmcts/github-management">github-management</a>, can be self serviced.</li>
<li>Add the new joiner to DTS Platform Operations group on <a href="https://github.com/hmcts/devops-azure-ad">devops-azure-ad</a></li>
<li>Add the new joiner to <a href="https://github.com/orgs/hmcts/teams/platform-operations/members">Platform Operations group</a></li>
<li>If and when required add user to <code>DTS Platform Operations SC</code> group in <a href="https://github.com/hmcts/devops-azure-ad">devops-azure-ad</a></li>
</ul>
